Now you see the difference
between that

00:22:08.720 --> 00:22:12.550 position:56%
and the previous thing I showed you.

00:22:12.550 --> 00:22:14.680
It's getting more Bodoni-like.

00:22:14.680 --> 00:22:21.200
So within this volume, this great
big folio volume there are lots

00:22:21.200 --> 00:22:24.780
of illustrations and there
are illustrations of battles

00:22:24.780 --> 00:22:34.840 position:56%
and uniforms and this is a Chinese
fair and this is an Arcadian theater

00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:40.400
so the festivities went
on for weeks and one

00:22:40.400 --> 00:22:47.660
of the performers was a local
soprano called affectionately La

00:22:47.660 --> 00:22:52.800
Bastardella because ancestry was
a little suspect but she sang

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:58.730
in operas in celebration and
these were operas by Gluck

00:22:58.730 --> 00:23:03.680
and take a very close
look at the next image.

00:23:03.680 --> 00:23:13.060
You know what's going on here?

00:23:13.060 --> 00:23:19.480
Bottom enhancement.

00:23:19.480 --> 00:23:21.910
&gt;&gt; False bottom?

