&gt;&gt; Valerie Lester:
Bottom enhancement.

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:27.020
The pot down on the bottom right
has the words Colla du Parma.

00:23:27.020 --> 00:23:33.700
Colla is glue and the man doing the
enhancement is his name is Giusepe

00:23:33.700 --> 00:23:35.000
du Colla.

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:38.910
A lot of play on words here
and he actually married,

00:23:38.910 --> 00:23:46.780
he married Lucrezia Aguiari
to give her her full name.

00:23:46.780 --> 00:23:57.180
And then at the end of the final
thing I've got is fireworks.

00:23:57.180 --> 00:23:59.960
Bodoni was starting by now.

00:23:59.960 --> 00:24:03.150
Fournier, gradually some of the
Fournier type was breaking down.

00:24:03.150 --> 00:24:08.000
Bodoni was cutting his own to
replace it so the shift is going

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:11.410
on between Fournier and Bodoni.

00:24:11.410 --> 00:24:17.260
Bodoni wanted to produce a specimen
book of ornaments so this page

00:24:17.260 --> 00:24:22.720
of his hand drawing of
ornaments which is also

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:30.350
at the Houghton Library at
Harvard and he produced this.

00:24:30.350 --> 00:24:36.320
This is a facsimile of
it and it's still very,

00:24:36.320 --> 00:24:38.620
this is still very like Fournier.

00:24:38.620 --> 00:24:41.180
Fournier has one of
these specimen books

00:24:41.180 --> 00:24:43.790
that has a cover very like this.

00:24:43.790 --> 00:24:52.520
And that's from the interior and
do any of you recognize this?

00:24:53.840 --> 00:25:00.750
It's actually modern day ITC
Bodoni designed by Sumner Stone.

00:25:00.750 --> 00:25:07.660
Some of you may know him and so
you can actually decorate your work

00:25:07.660 --> 00:25:10.850
with this.

00:25:10.850 --> 00:25:15.280
This is not Bodoni's
studio but his contemporary

00:25:15.280 --> 00:25:21.330
so his printworks would have
looked very much like this.

00:25:21.330 --> 00:25:23.110
People would have been
wearing the same things.

00:25:23.110 --> 00:25:25.960
They would have been using
the same kind of equipment.

00:25:25.960 --> 00:25:33.390
There are big windows that face out
