00:25:47.020 --> 00:25:51.300
huge collection, huge
collection of punches really,

00:25:51.300 --> 00:25:53.420
really wonderful collection.

00:25:53.420 --> 00:26:02.000
These are Bodoni's
matrices and molds.

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:06.040
