incredible volume he had just

00:39:02.850 --> 00:39:13.480
produced which included 150
different types in many,

00:39:13.480 --> 00:39:19.280
many exotic languages and the
Pope was deeply impressed.

00:39:19.280 --> 00:39:23.600 position:56%
On his way back to Rome after what
