00:39:23.600 --> 00:39:32.260 position:56%
moment for him crowning Napoleon he
stopped in Parma, went to see Bodoni

00:39:32.260 --> 00:39:37.670
and said, "Okay, can you
do better than this?"

00:39:37.670 --> 00:39:39.860
Well could he?

00:39:39.860 --> 00:39:41.160
Yeah. Of course he could.

